## Requirements

scml-vis requires Python 3.8 or above.

## Installation

With `pip`:
```bash
python3 -m pip install scml-vis
```

With [`pipx`](https://github.com/pipxproject/pipx):
```bash
python3 -m pip install --user pipx

pipx install scml-vis
```

